&ldquo;We want to move to a 4-3-3 but for that you need a lot of specificity in every position but now in 5/6 positions we don&rsquo;t have it. The aggressiveness, the effectiveness, the amount of steals we make in opposition half I think we have been very steady against some big clubs&rdquo;.<br />
<br />
&ldquo;I think that what we miss is in the opponents area and the last part of the pitch. We have to find the key in the attack, that last decision, that last pass, that last cross to create a goal situation, a goal, a shot, a corner, etc.&rdquo;

